HEADWORD: Macowanites
<hw>Macowanites</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A
stout-stemmed genus of fungi belonging to the family
<fam>Secotiaceae</fam> having fruiting bodies that never expand
completely.</def>⟦br⟧
